articles.author: Andrew Lawrence
articles.title: 'THE WITCH IS DEAD': disgraced Daniel Snyder finally exits the stage - The Guardian
articles.description: Dan Snyder’s record $6.05bn sale of the Washington Commanders will mark the end of a 24-year tenure defined by scandal, dysfunction and ineptitude
articles.content: The long national nightmare could soon be over. NFL fans in and around the nations capital havent stopped buzzing since word spread this week that Washington Commanders owner Daniel Snyder had agreed… [+7159 chars]
